# Testing Guide

## Test 1 – Record Visibility
1. Login as Employee A
2. Create HR request
3. Login as Employee B
4. Confirm access denied

## Test 2 – HR Agent
1. Login as HR Agent
2. Confirm visibility of all records
3. Confirm SSN field not visible

## Test 3 – HR Admin
1. Login as HR Admin
2. Confirm SSN field visible

## Test 4 – REST API
1. Call API as Employee → 403
2. Call API as Agent → 201
3. Call API as Admin → can include SSN field
